title: DIVA Magazine - May 2014  UK
description:
DIVA Magazine - May 2014  UK

100 Pages | True PDF | English | 34 MB 


The UK's leading lesbian lifestyle magazine looks better than ever, thanks to a fabulous redesign. Packed monthly with news, innovative features, celebrity interviews, an arts, social scene, shopping AND travel agenda, plus the UK's most comprehensive listings section, DIVA is a monthly must-have for gay and bi women worldwide. All this, together with some of the hottest girls around, make DIVA a magazine you'll want to devour from cover to cover!
